<ps_doc title="PlatSoft Grape Manual" titlepage="yes" tocpage="yes" description="Developer's guide to using the PlatSoft Grape Framework">
	<h1 id="sec-grape-auth">Authentication</h1>
	<h2>auth_info</h2>
	Fields used:
		totp_status: "pending verification", "ok", 
		totp_key
		password_reset_code


<h2>Access Roles</h2>
If a user is logged in, they will always belong to the role "all".
If a user is not authenticated, they will belong to the roles "guest".

